text: Maida Vale School is a coeducational, independent school in London, England.School Search | Maida Vale School Founded in 2019, it is the fourth school opened by the Gardener Schools Group, who purchased the former City of Westminster College building located at 18 Saltram Crescent.Harrow Road Ward Labour Action Report – June 2019 ==References== ==External links== * School Website Category:Educational institutions established in 2019 Category:Education in the City of Westminster Category:Independent co- educational schools in London Category:Independent schools in the City of Westminster
